invalid type: string "## Failure mode analysis is highly valuable\n\nInstead of asking only whether systems failed, it is often more useful to ask why they failed.\n\nExamples include:\n\n* retrieval failures\n* reasoning failures\n* orchestration failures\n* prompt failures\n* context construction issues\n* infrastructure issues\n* UX problems\n\niteration instead of relying only on intuition.\nĸ